name: Ceiba - Tree of Life I
description:
1/8

One of the most representative specimens of the southern hemisphere, the Ceiba Speciosa also known as Palo Borracho. Popular stories tell there is a unique one with special powers and dimensions. 
Climbing up and passing through its thorns it is believed one can reach a pale pink garden suspended in the heights, where the bliss is infinite and the stay is forever.
